headline.main: Republicans in Maine, Utah Want Trump to Undo Monuments
headline.print_headline: Republicans in Maine, Utah Want Trump to Undo Monuments

lead_paragraph: Republican leaders in Maine and Utah are asking President Donald Trump to step into uncharted territory and rescind national monument designations made by his predecessor.
